CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 15, 1939, pg. 7, reads: "Wednesday Bridge Club Hostesses to Beautiful Holiday Event at Loendi - Scenes at the Wednesday Bridge Club's Easter Monday party at Loendi... Center, the hostesses, left to right: Marion Bannister, Marie Meredith, Myrtle Britton, Gertrude McKain, Hazel Lee, Dorothy Black. Seated: Adelaide Jordan and Helen Lee... Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Hostesses for bridge club, standing from left: Marion Bannister, Marie Meredith, Myrtle Britton, Gertrude McKain, Hazel Lee, Dorothy Black; seated: Adelaide Jordan, and Helen Lee, posed in Loendi Club
